thread.title: Carl Peterson
thread.title_full: Public Storage reviewed by Carl Peterson

author: Carl Peterson
title: Carl Peterson
text: The property manager was very helpful; the process was quick. My storage unit is exactly what I wanted. The price is a little high, but it's competitive for the area. If the price was lower, I would consider keeping the unit long term, but at $130/month, that doesn't make sense.
